  OUT AddressFormatId	varchar(2)
)
DYNAMIC RESULT SETS 1 
LANGUAGE SQL 
SPECIFIC [SCLIBRARY].CMM_ExcGetCountryAddrFormat 
NOT DETERMINISTIC 
